ba&#351;la&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Lukman m&ouml;h&uuml;m funksi&yacute;alary&#328;
g&ouml;rkezijilerine baha ber&yacute;&auml;r (a&#328;y&#328; barlygy, dem aly&#351;
tizligi, gany&#328; kislorod bilen do&yacute;ma derejesi, impulsy&#328;
&yacute;ygylygy we a&yacute;ratynlyklary), barlag ge&ccedil;ir&yacute;&auml;r
we kliniki suraty&#328; be&yacute;leki seb&auml;plerini hem &#351;u&#328;a
me&#328;ze&yacute;&auml;r insult keseline (TBI-ni &yacute;ok etmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in kell&auml;ni&#328; &yacute;um&#351;ak dokumalaryny barlamak,
giperglikemi&yacute;a &yacute;agda&yacute;yny &yacute;ok etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in
gl&yacute;ukozany&#328; derejesini kesgitlemek we &#351;.m.).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
