color:black'>Kernigi&#328; alamaty - lukman hassany&#328; el-a&yacute;agyny
eg&yacute;&auml;r, &#351;ondan so&#328; n&auml;sagdan ony d&uuml;zetm&auml;ge
synany&#351;magyny ha&yacute;y&#351; ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>My&#351;sany&#328;
&yacute;okary sesi seb&auml;pli bu m&uuml;mkin d&auml;l bolup
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Oksipital my&#351;salary&#328; berkligi - oksipital
my&#351;salary&#328; sesini&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy e&#328;egi&#328;
d&ouml;&#351;&uuml;ne getirilmezligine seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Brudzinskini&#328; alamaty - e&#328;egi d&ouml;&#351;&uuml;ne
getirjek bolanda a&yacute;agy&#328; islegsiz egilmegi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Brudzinskini&#328; alamaty orta&ccedil;a -
d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328; s&uuml;&#328;k&uuml;ne basylanda
n&auml;sagy&#328; a&yacute;aklary b&ouml;wrek bogunlaryna egilip, bedene
&ccedil;ekil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Brudzinskini&#328; alamaty - &ouml;&#328; egilen a&yacute;agy
d&uuml;zetmek synany&#351;ygy be&yacute;leki a&yacute;agy&#328;yzy bedene
&ccedil;ekm&auml;ge seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a
g&ouml;zlegleri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gany&#328; umumy der&#328;ewi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Biohimiki gan barlagy (ALT, AST, gl&yacute;ukoza, jemi holesterin,
trigliseridler).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Koagulogramma (APTT, fibrinogen, INR) garynla&#351;ma ulgamyny,
gany&#328; fibrinolitiki i&#351;je&#328;ligini &ouml;wrenmegi&#328; usulydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gemorragiki insult &yacute;a-da subarahnoid ganamaga
&#351;&uuml;bhelen&yacute;&auml;n bolsa, serebrospinal suwuklygy&#328;
der&#328;ewi ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Nusga almak lomber ponksion
arkaly amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu &yacute;agda&yacute;da
serebrospinal suwuklykda k&ouml;p sanly eritrositler we orta&ccedil;a
lenfositler bolar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Instrumental synag</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>KT (hasaplanan tomografi&yacute;a) rentgen &#351;&ouml;hlelerini
ulanyp be&yacute;nini&#328; gatlak-gatlagyna esaslan&yacute;an
ne&yacute;roimage usulydyr.&nbsp;I&#351;emiki we gemorragiki urgulary
tapawutlandyrmak, t&auml;sir eden &yacute;eri, ululygyny we
lokalizasi&yacute;asyny bahalandyrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;KT-i&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen damar n&auml;sazlyklary,
anewrizmalar we stenozlar, &#351;e&yacute;le hem be&yacute;nini&#328;
be&yacute;leki patologi&yacute;alary (&ccedil;i&#351;ler, &yacute;okan&ccedil;
we &ccedil;i&#351;me prosesi, be&yacute;nini&#328; &#351;ikeslenmegi)
a&yacute;ryl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>MRI (magnit-rezonans tomografi&yacute;asy) insult diagnozynda hem
ulanyl&yacute;an usul.&nbsp;Birme&#328;ze&#351; anykla&yacute;y&#351;
&auml;hmi&yacute;eti bar, be&yacute;ni dokumasyny&#328; gurlu&#351;
bozulmalaryna baha bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;KT-den has
takyk, be&yacute;nini&#328; zeperlenmelerini
anykla&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Synagy&#328; dowamlylygy seb&auml;pli has az
ulanyl&yacute;ar (30-45 minut).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Bo&yacute;n damarlaryny&#328; ultrases barlagy da&#351;arky we
intrakranial damarlary&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yna (damar
&ouml;s&uuml;&#351;ini&#328; patologi&yacute;asy, gemodinamiki ta&yacute;dan
&auml;hmi&yacute;etli stenozlar, aterosklerotik ny&#351;anlary&#328; bolmagy,
gan a&yacute;lany&#351; tizligi) baha berm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>EchoCG - insulty&#328; kardioemboliki h&auml;si&yacute;ete
e&yacute;e bolandygyna &#351;&uuml;bhelen&yacute;&auml;n bolsa,
&yacute;&uuml;regi&#328; ultrases barlagy ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Epilepsi&yacute;any aradan a&yacute;yrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
n&auml;sagda tutga&yacute; bolanda EEG (elektroensefalogramma)
ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Serebral angiografi&yacute;a be&yacute;nini&#328; anewrizmalaryny
we subarahnoid gan akmalaryny &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;K&ouml;p halatlarda, CT we MRI tehniki ta&yacute;dan
el&yacute;eterli bolmadyk mahaly &yacute;erine &yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>M&ouml;h&uuml;m funksi&yacute;alary&#328; we organlary&#328;
bozulmalaryny gyssagly d&uuml;zetmek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>organiki kem&ccedil;iligi azaltmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>bolup biljek kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&yacute;itirilen funksi&yacute;alary b&ouml;lekle&yacute;in
&yacute;a-da doly dikeltmek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;
&yacute;oly we gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Insult
&#351;&uuml;bhelen&yacute;&auml;n bolsa, n&auml;sag kellesini &yacute;okary
galdyryp keseligine &yacute;erle&#351;meli.&nbsp;Kislorody&#328; akymyny
&uuml;pj&uuml;n etmek, dem aly&#351; &yacute;ollaryny keseki zatlardan we
protezlerden bo&#351;atmak, a&#328;y&#328; bozulan &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda
dili&#328; yza &ccedil;ekilmegine g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek zerurdyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keselhanany&#328;
tapgyrynda hassalar basy&#351; &yacute;arasyny&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in her 3-4 sagatdan bir gapdala ge&ccedil;meli.&nbsp;A&#351;aky
b&ouml;leklerde elastik bandajlary&#328; we joraplary&#328; ulanylmagy,
a&#351;aky b&ouml;lekleri&#328; damarlarynda trombozy&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak we &ouml;&yacute;ken emboli&yacute;asy (PE)
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykmagyny&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Trombolitiki bejergi, arterial okkl&yacute;uzi&yacute;a gan
damarlaryny&#328; &yacute;a-da embolusy&#328; d&ouml;remeginden so&#328;,
i&#351;emiki insult &uuml;&ccedil;in
g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Keseli&#328; d&ouml;remeginden ilkinji 6
sagady&#328; dowamynda ulanylyp bilner.&nbsp;Bu maksatlar &uuml;&ccedil;in
a&#351;akdaky dermanlar ulanyl&yacute;ar: alteplase, prourokinase, tenecteplase
we &#351;.m.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antihipertansif dermanlar - ACE inhibitorlary, kalsi&yacute; kanal
blokatorlary, beta-blokatorlar, angiotensin II reseptor antagonistleri kliniki
tejribede ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Uly be&yacute;nini&#328;
giperf&yacute;uzi&yacute;asyny&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in gan basy&#351;yny&#328; peselmegi gaty &ccedil;alt bolmaly
d&auml;ldir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Newroprotektiki dermanlar, gurlu&#351; zeperlenmelerinde nerw
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerine gora&yacute;jy t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;n
dermanlardyr.&nbsp;Antioksidantlary, kalsi&yacute; kanal blokatorlaryny,
nootropikleri, postinaptiki gl&yacute;utamat ingibitorlaryny we &#351;.m.
ulan&yacute;arlar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antiplatelet seri&#351;deleri trombositleri&#328; we gyzyl gan
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerini&#328; &yacute;ygry&#351; ukybyny
peseld&yacute;&auml;r, damarlary&#328; d&ouml;remegini&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni al&yacute;ar we bar bolan gan damarlaryny&#328; dargamagyna
seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Olar i&#351;emiki insulty&#328; bejergisi,
tromboemboliki kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antikonwulsanlar epileptiki tutga&yacute;lar &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Steroid d&auml;l &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y dermanlar
(NSAID) bedeni&#328; gyzgynlygy febril bahalaryna (38 gradusdan &yacute;okary)
&yacute;okarlananda ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antiemetiki dermanlar - uzak we dowamly dispeptiki alamatlar
&uuml;&ccedil;in (&yacute;&uuml;rek bulanma we gusmak).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Kislorod bejergisi - &yacute;okary mukdarda kislorod bilen gaz
garyndysyny&#328; dem almagy.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>N&auml;sagy&#328; da&#351;arky
dem aly&#351; i&#351;ini kadala&#351;dyrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Adaty &auml;he&#328;i saklamak we my&#351;salary&#328;
