&yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Gematoma bo&#351;lugyna &yacute;&ouml;rite
fibrinolitiki derman sanjym edil&yacute;&auml;r, ol bolsa damarlary
ered&yacute;&auml;r, &#351;ondan so&#328; mazmuny islen&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

