</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gematomany a&ccedil;-a&ccedil;an a&yacute;yrmak - gematomany
a&ccedil;-a&ccedil;an a&yacute;yrmak.&nbsp;Gematomany doly a&yacute;yrmak bir
amalda amala a&#351;yrylyp bilner.&nbsp;&#350;ol bir wagty&#328;
